\paragraph{GEMV/GEMM boundary and padding fix.}
Condition~B residuals stem from a secondary source: cuBLAS dispatches to a
GEMV kernel at $M\!=\!1$ and a GEMM kernel at $M\!\ge\!2$, and FP32
